data.description: Completely remodeled/updated plus new roof in Northwoods! Smart house with Ring doorbell and security. 3 bedrooms with 2 full baths, breakfast area off kitchen, family room with fireplace is open to dining area. LVP flooring throughout, slab granite in kitchen and bathrooms with deep soaking tubs. Freshly painted interior, exterior painted 2 years ago.
